                     <p>Signed and sealed bond by Arundell <lb/> and Richard Scawen on a printed form, <lb/> promising to pay £200 to Edward <lb/> Hinton, goldsmith of London. <lb/> 1 p.; 30 x 19 cm. <lb/> Witnessed by Claudius Pettit and <lb/> George Bucknor, with their <lb/> signatures.</p>
